org.pepstock.charba.client.controllers

Class NativeJsControllerHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.controllers.NativeJsControllerHelper

  • @JsType(isNative=true,
        name="CharbaJsControllerHelper",
        namespace="<global>")
final class NativeJsControllerHelper
extends Object
    This is a Java native object which is wrapping a CHARBA java script object implementation with some utilities to manage CHART.JS controllers.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
